NAME 

	useradd & delete    : add and delete user
        groupadd & delete   : add group and delete
        passwd & usermod -1 : chande information user
	usermod -g          : add specific user to specific group

SYNOPSIS 

        useradd[USERNAME]
        userdel[USERNAME]
        groupadd[GROUPNAME]
        groupdel[GROUPNAME]
        passwd[PASSWORD]
        usermod -l[USERNAME]
        usermod -g[USERNAME]

DESCRIPTION

	This task make  number of instructions : adduser, deleteuser,
        addgroup and can delete it,
        change user information,
        and add specific user to specific group


